	<Title>
		Abortion: Does it affect subsequent pregnancies?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Abortion isn&apos;t likely to cause infertility or pregnancy complications in a subsequent pregnancy.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Could an abortion increase the risk of problems in a subsequent pregnancy?
	</Question>
